name: Moroccan Kabab Recipe | Masala TV
ingredients: Ingredients for Moroccan Kabab Recipe: Boneless chicken ½ kg cubes Raw papaya grinded 2tbsp Salt 1 tsp Yogurt ½ cup Ginger garlic 1 tbsp Roasted crushed cumin 1 tsp Lemon juice ¼ cup Oil ¼ cup Black pepper 1 tsp Cinnamon powder 1 tsp Red crush pepper 1 tsp Paprika 1 tsp Turmeric ¼ tsp
instructions: Marinate chicken cubes with raw papaya, crushed red pepper Add black pepper, and paprika, cinnamon powder turmeric Add cumin, salt, yogurt, oil, lemon juice, ginger garlic, leave it for few hours. Put on skewers bake in oven on 180 degrees for 25 mins give dum of coal. Serve with onion rings.
